<style>
    .mail{
        background-color: rgb(224, 224, 224);
        padding-left:20%;
        padding-right:20%;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>


<div class="mail">
    <h3> Hello {{ user }} </h3>

    <p> You recently requested a new password. Use the link below to continue the change. </p>
    <p> Keep in mind this token is only valid for 1 hour. </p>
    
    <a href="http://localhost:3000/profile/resetPassword/{{token}}">Reset my password</a>


    <p> If you didn't request this, please ignore this email. </p>
    <p> Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one. </p>
</div>

